Q: 展示2023-2024年中，Aircompany North-west在St Louis Metro-East/Shafer Field的航班数量及主要使用的飞机型号。
SQL:
SELECT
    c.supplier_name,
    b.aircraft_model_name,
    COUNT(*) AS num,
    (SELECT COUNT(*)
     FROM zts_plane_flight a
     LEFT JOIN aircraft_details b_sub ON a.pure_reg = b_sub.pure_reg
     LEFT JOIN supplier_details c_sub ON b_sub.supplier_id = c_sub.supplier_id
     WHERE (a.dep_icao = "IL48" OR a.arr_icao = "IL48")
       AND a.arr_date >= '2023-11-01 00:00:00'
       AND a.arr_date < '2024-11-02 00:00:00'
       AND c_sub.supplier_id = "1109") AS total_flight
FROM
    zts_plane_flight a
LEFT JOIN
    aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
LEFT JOIN
    supplier_details c ON b.supplier_id = c.supplier_id
WHERE
    (a.dep_icao = "IL48" OR a.arr_icao = "IL48")
    AND c.supplier_id = "1109"
    AND a.arr_date >= '2023-11-01 00:00:00'
    AND a.arr_date < '2024-11-01 00:00:00'
GROUP BY
    c.supplier_name, b.aircraft_model_name
ORDER BY num desc
LIMIT 3;

    c.supplier_name,
    b.aircraft_model_name,
    COUNT(*) AS num,
    (SELECT COUNT(*)
     FROM zts_plane_flight a
     LEFT JOIN aircraft_details b_sub ON a.pure_reg = b_sub.pure_reg
     LEFT JOIN supplier_details c_sub ON b_sub.supplier_id = c_sub.supplier_id
     WHERE (a.dep_icao = "CCS3" OR a.arr_icao = "CCS3")
       AND a.arr_date >= '2023-11-01 00:00:00'
       AND a.arr_date < '2024-11-02 00:00:00'
       AND c_sub.supplier_id = "1112") AS total_flight
FROM
    zts_plane_flight a
LEFT JOIN
    aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
LEFT JOIN
    supplier_details c ON b.supplier_id = c.supplier_id
WHERE
    (a.dep_icao = "CCS3" OR a.arr_icao = "CCS3")
    AND c.supplier_id = "1112"
    AND a.arr_date >= '2023-11-01 00:00:00'
    AND a.arr_date < '2024-11-01 00:00:00'
GROUP BY
    c.supplier_name, b.aircraft_model_name
ORDER BY num desc
LIMIT 3;
